Grammar

    0 $accept: Start $end

    1 Start: /* empty */
    2      | Exp
    3      | HELP
    4      | QUIT

    5 Exp: Primary
    6    | Exp OP_ADD Primary
    7    | Exp OP_SUB Primary
    8    | Exp OP_MUL Primary
    9    | Exp OP_DIV Primary
   10    | Exp OP_POW Primary
   11    | Exp OP_MOD Primary
   12    | Exp OP_FACT
   13    | M_SIN Primary
   14    | M_COS Primary
   15    | M_TAN Primary
   16    | M_COTAN Primary
