   18    | M_LOG2 Primary
   19    | M_LOGE Primary
   20    | M_SQRT Primary
   21    | M_CEIL Primary
   22    | M_FLOOR Primary
   23    | OP_SUB Primary
   24    | OP_ADD Primary

   25 Primary: VARIABLE
   26        | VARIABLE OP_EQU Exp
   27        | Constant
   28        | LPAR Exp RPAR

   29 Constant: INT_VAL
   30         | DBL_VAL
   31         | CONST_PI
   32         | CONST_E


